creator: MST LLC
descriptionHtml:
MST Lab 24 is a web service + mobile app. Be mobile, work with any device!
Working with our service, you get a functionally optimized service with an intuitive interface.  

Why MST Lab 24?
· Cost-effective – the only thing you need to test the full version is registration;
· Cloud solution - available for smartphones, tablets, desktop computers;
· Safe – secure technologies to protect network connections.

The service is ideal for organizations with field employees, regularly visiting customers for stock checkout, merchandising on the shelves, control of promos and other marketing activities.
The solution allows to simplify field work - step-by-step algorithm of store report creation minimizes errors and enables effect
descriptionShort: Service to connect your field workers and office
